text: Audun Hadler-Olsen (born 6 January 1969) is a Norwegian rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Norway Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bergen
